Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《僵尸国度》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去和大队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送摩菲到实验室去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后找到治愈僵尸病毒的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个谎话  而且这谎话会害死我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也情愿因相信这个谎话而死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总好过没有信仰地苟且活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  艾迪  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-发生什么了  -我知道那些闪回是怎么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谁也不会丢下其他人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为你而回  我以后也会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定市民Z让我们下到这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是死是活  是人还是丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死人一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边  这边  这边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}歌词改编自一段美国跳长绳时唱的童谣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰姑娘穿上了一身黄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到了楼上去亲暖男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她嗑完了药
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又丢了节操
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来数数她宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几只丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能给他们个痛快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:01:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那别动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  原来是奇葩二人组啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞毛线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是奇葩...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥从来  我是说真的  一百万年做梦也想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有机会能再看到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市民Z让你们到这的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  他说这有食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说有个叫切斯特的人能帮我们逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊他也这么跟我们说了  真怀疑有没有这么个人    
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  这个人应该能帮得上忙  我们先往那边走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么了这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她之前被一个带刺的铁丝网伤到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在伤口都感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们找到切斯特了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  切斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人在末世过得不是很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩在外面的时候都发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她弄明白了一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道  有些事情在脑海中就是挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到他们了吗  找到我的小队了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沃伦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  这真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们的老朋友市民Z
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪还是一如既往那么美艳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定就是麦克了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵  我原本以为你个子会再高一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么乳臭未干也真是出乎我意料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩菲  上前头来让我看清楚你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来不错  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们猜怎么着  我这里有个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加利福尼亚重新上线了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分都还活着也连上网了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们准备好迎接你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研发疫苗之梦没有破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务继续  衷心感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这消息不错是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息应该是有一包奥利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和几加仑的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个大厅下面左手边的那个房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面应该有你们需要的所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再次见到你们我真是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴你能见到我们还活着  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中情局黑牢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是水刑和《猎杀本·拉登》里那样的黑牢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是切斯特告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为挺明显的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老家伙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  真不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伦  这段路开慢点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是孩子  这是个被碾到的僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距盐湖城251英里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十点钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来一个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伦停车  只是个孩子而已  停车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别  你弄疼我了  别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该哪哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  前面这孩子还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是个穿着古怪花衬衫一脸悲伤的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有点口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我水壶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以叫我罗伯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈知道你自己一个人在外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去盐湖城看我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经长大了  我终于可以见我爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路太远了  况且路上也不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路不算远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布纳恩和达克斯已经到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盐湖城已经被僵尸占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经长大了  可以去见你的父亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还有个事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的食物吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮帮我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友海伦可以帮到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能告诉我们他们住在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带我们去找你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开车带你去盐湖城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩菲  让个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  小伙子  我叫麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}蒙蒂塞洛  犹他州
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}非请莫入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着好像没人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  你先下去侦查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到车里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着  别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们毫无恶意  我们只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停停停  别开火  先听我把话说完好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你说她们很友善  山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开火  求你们别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的孩子在我们车上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆跟我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海伦女士  没事的  他们只是想找些食物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们人不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你  山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进去找你妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信她现在急着想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们能带他回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我们的孩子得了幽居病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后决定要外出探险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在到了仁慈姐妹会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  我们赶时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想留下也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必须得留下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是不是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想留下  你们就必须分开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只让女人和孩子进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的朋友可以进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但男人们必须待在墙外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给你们二十四小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可以休息  吃东西  然后上路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你怎么称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海伦  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯塔·沃伦中尉  密苏里国民警卫队的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会照顾她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  这糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的腿感染了  带他去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看看我的胡萝卜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己种的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个  看这里面所有的花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里  我们自己种蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面我们还有鸡和牛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛  你们有牛奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶  黄油  酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们来说最重要的是青霉素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾米自己做的  她以前是药剂师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厨房的琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会告诉你们  哪里可以清洁一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  我希望你能一起来吃午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了  应该是  手背  手掌  拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右  然后左
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我很久没玩过这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈很久之前教过我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她人好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是的  她人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁建立了这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是预见到大灾变的到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里简直完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我丈夫建立的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的处世哲学是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该绝对地自给自足  脱离尘世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像其他人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉娜和埃米琳是我的好姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚蒙死后  我们只有彼此与这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们发现这些女人前  她们都很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在她们安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再吃点草莓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃了   我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去找一下卡桑德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看她怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们种的胡萝卜吗  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好些了吗  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得山姆和我们说他要去哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去盐湖城找他爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米有个比山姆大一些的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也去盐湖城找爸爸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩都在  而男孩长到13岁都离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们看起来很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩  有点幸福过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太善良的人总会吓到我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好起来  我们一起离开这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的女人让我毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个金发女人一直盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们  可千万别低估了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是一块抢手的大肥肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  做好你的本分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里面真的只有女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  小万万  你好好幻想一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许只能想想罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克  有一点我不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都死到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们可以问问她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自天堂的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是派吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝莓派  额...  我我我...我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个人去哪了  那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发和眼睛...  他...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一万  别让人打扰哥  末世结束再叫醒哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去给他送一块派
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃派吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子  走开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  有人让你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯呐嗯呐  姐了解  姐全都了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爹地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要我的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我又很想吃派
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食人族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉你遇到了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的想说我很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他无法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动物的本能掌控了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滥杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强奸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又是这个瘟疫  这个病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄性荷尔蒙才是地球上最毒的毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你挺过了这一切  来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始我就遇到了麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看是他运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以告诉我  告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看开吧  释怀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能告诉你件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也不会遭遇这样的惨剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方  我们姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用得上你这样的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明  有本事  心地善良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和其他人不一样  你很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有新姐妹加入我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎  欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不会有人伤害你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们建立了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受男性暴力侵害的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们会惩罚那些施暴者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬我啊  婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好名字  你用着合适
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候让你见识见识正义了  婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢伤女人  你就得死  这就是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.98,0:23:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎说外面还有两个姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以帮我们解救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:23:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃伦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都有可能像她们一样需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加入
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.95,0:24:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.30,0:24:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要支持我的姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得跟这些人撇清关系  小伙子们  上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.91,0:24:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克  等会  大哥  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.79,0:24:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.52,0:24:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.72,0:24:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们不会就这样扔下我们不管了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  艾迪不会离开我的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.87,0:24:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.48,0:24:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚才就离开你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.06,0:25:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到什么麻烦了吗  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这样很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.34,0:25:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么漂亮的两个姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.90,0:25:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能独自上路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.15,0:25:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面可不怎么安全
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说说你们要往哪个方向走
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.72,0:25:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侧三轮上的小伙子能帮你们检查引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.21,0:25:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手举起来  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.11,0:25:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的小把戏就到此结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.19,0:25:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  别这样  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.96,0:25:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他们不是一伙的  他们只不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.39,0:25:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我被困住了  他们把我救出来的  -闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.42,0:25:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得美  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.31,0:26:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪  别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.84,0:26:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是个讲理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.08,0:26:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事情我们可以好好商量
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.10,0:26:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你直接告诉我你想要什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.75,0:26:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来问你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.05,0:26:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个女孩是自愿跟着你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.02,0:26:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.64,0:26:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.31,0:26:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.25,0:26:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有个挂包  里面装的全是奥施康定[止痛药]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.06,0:26:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以全拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.49,0:26:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.97,0:26:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有怒气冲冲的婊子不做交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.42,0:26:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.48,0:26:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  过来帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.73,0:26:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸张正义的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.11,0:26:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉一个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.46,0:26:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要致命伤  但不要爆头
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.72,0:26:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余的人自然就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.10,0:27:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.62,0:27:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀另一个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.26,0:27:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.14,0:27:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓  不是我干的  求你了  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.69,0:27:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有必要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.54,0:27:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.18,0:27:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想与我为敌的  好妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  我  我发誓  我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.98,0:27:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.30,0:27:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得食人族绑架了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.54,0:27:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得托拜亚斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.80,0:27:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得他绑架了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.67,0:27:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  不不  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.49,0:27:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.50,0:28:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.07,0:28:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得离开这
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.08,0:28:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我看到那头熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.76,0:28:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都不算事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.11,0:28:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连僵尸熊都不算事了  那还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.64,0:28:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要见她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.66,0:28:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在一个很奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.70,0:28:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去过那
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.56,0:28:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将她带出来可不是件容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.28,0:28:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  但是没有她我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.97,0:28:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.49,0:29:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽全力将她带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你可能还是要做出一个选择
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.09,0:29:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.55,0:29:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我杀死自己的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.05,0:29:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得自由的时候也有同样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.20,0:29:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当时也声称是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.47,0:29:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从小到大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.77,0:29:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.40,0:29:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是好人  是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.03,0:29:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上帝的恩赐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.02,0:29:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我差点死于生第五个孩子之后
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.82,0:29:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就开始不再相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再生孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.63,0:29:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要他了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.27,0:29:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些想法不符合那些信条
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.26,0:29:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他就打我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.58,0:30:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的鼻子  胳膊还有肋骨都被他打折了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.61,0:30:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还不算最糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.42,0:30:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的姐妹们还有更惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.06,0:30:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就得离开
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.30,0:30:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见艾迪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.54,0:30:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会在出去的路上找到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.40,0:30:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.87,0:30:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.20,0:30:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.98,0:30:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从外面进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.44,0:30:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道外面是什么样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.42,0:30:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也...  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.35,0:30:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.20,0:30:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到无动于衷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.68,0:30:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.40,0:30:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你承受得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.20,0:30:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.31,0:31:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.29,0:31:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平静
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.03,0:31:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.65,0:31:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我们家庭中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.30,0:31:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能离开麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.05,0:31:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.14,0:31:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.52,0:31:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你爱他  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.09,0:31:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让你眼睁睁看着他死会更痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总有一天会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.79,0:31:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你将会是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.50,0:31:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他"施与仁慈"的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.86,0:31:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.25,0:31:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.87,0:32:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.52,0:32:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来教你怎么跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.15,0:32:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.40,0:32:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.81,0:32:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找个地方说几句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.19,0:32:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.61,0:32:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去有些怪异  毕竟一个僵尸...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.79,0:32:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  麦克  里面...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.05,0:32:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面很美
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.39,0:32:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你能看见就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.13,0:32:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我也希望能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.47,0:32:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟外面的世界截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.47,0:32:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我有了安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.34,0:32:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很久没有这样的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.04,0:32:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.69,0:33:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.75,0:33:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说  离开那里应该挺难的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.97,0:33:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我想跟你谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.28,0:33:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.58,0:33:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撑不下去了  麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.02,0:33:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  艾迪...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.84,0:33:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟你一起留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.42,0:33:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.41,0:33:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.09,0:33:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你  我什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.37,0:33:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  艾迪  艾迪  拜托  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.78,0:33:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  我...  你不能...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.88,0:33:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  我真的很爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.49,0:34:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再回去  看着你死
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.99,0:34:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.14,0:34:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你会死
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.49,0:34:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.13,0:34:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望留存在我脑海里的是你现在的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.49,0:34:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  我不能再夺去我心爱之人的生命了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.26,0:34:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不走  我也不会走的  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.93,0:34:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.32,0:34:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对大家都好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.66,0:34:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  艾迪  等等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.71,0:34:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩菲怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.70,0:34:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.30,0:34:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过  怀揣着信仰死去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.96,0:34:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总好过无所信仰地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.76,0:34:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.77,0:34:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我  看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.92,0:34:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解  我懂  你...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.51,0:34:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈的事让你很难过  人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.49,0:34:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事太可怕了  简直是个悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.16,0:34:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你会熬过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.27,0:34:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.73,0:35:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个好人  你很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.34,0:35:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很强  你不需要海伦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.97,0:35:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么脑残邪教
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.65,0:35:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.70,0:35:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  艾迪  你不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.06,0:35:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麦克  -你不能离开我  这样很疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.59,0:35:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麦克  -艾迪  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.68,0:35:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麦克  放开我  -艾迪  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.52,0:35:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.56,0:35:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麦克  -你没考虑清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄疼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.19,0:35:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.46,0:35:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.63,0:35:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.44,0:35:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.34,0:35:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.31,0:35:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.11,0:35:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.04,0:35:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.13,0:35:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.06,0:35:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.46,0:35:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.64,0:35:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我们说话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.49,0:36:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.04,0:36:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们受够你的帮助了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.46,0:36:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.60,0:36:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.86,0:36:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.35,0:36:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.72,0:36:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.70,0:36:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩菲在哪里  我们需要帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.26,0:36:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟那个女孩还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.03,0:36:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.70,0:36:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派对结束了 大家要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.68,0:36:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪里弄来香烟的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.25,0:36:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.19,0:36:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.63,0:37:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要上路了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.67,0:37:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  站起来走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.87,0:37:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.19,0:37:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则她不会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.88,0:37:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.58,0:37:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  告诉她们
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.94,0:37:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你告诉我的告诉她们
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.12,0:37:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打定主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.92,0:37:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟海伦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.48,0:37:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.48,0:37:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大门出事了  我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留在这里  你会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.54,0:37:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪  我知道这地方感觉很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.77,0:37:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.89,0:37:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇到托拜亚斯时  也是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.38,0:37:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.03,0:37:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.65,0:37:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起经历了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.68,0:38:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪生·卡弗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.18,0:38:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.68,0:38:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.92,0:38:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被卷入的这桩事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.15,0:38:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做出了你的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.42,0:38:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也都做出了努力
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.35,0:38:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在是时候离开了  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.95,0:38:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全部
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.21,0:38:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这现在就是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.35,0:38:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.98,0:38:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.09,0:38:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.96,0:38:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那高个子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.35,0:38:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的头头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.90,0:38:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这  你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.63,0:38:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.31,0:38:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.14,0:38:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你乖乖把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.03,0:39:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你乖乖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.87,0:39:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们就好好聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.25,0:39:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们和和气气的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.85,0:39:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.24,0:39:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扣扳机可是出了名的快
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.61,0:39:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.10,0:39:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她绝对跟着我一起陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.03,0:39:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.12,0:39:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.97,0:39:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.93,0:39:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.12,0:39:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.12,0:39:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会来的  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.82,0:39:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  她会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.31,0:39:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.28,0:39:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.29,0:39:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.32,0:40:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.92,0:40:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远爱你  麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.28,0:40:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们不来这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.13,0:40:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们不能分开
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.64,0:40:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.41,0:40:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.02,0:40:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢射他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.76,0:40:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个警告  快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.21,0:40:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁姑奶奶们心情好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.18,0:40:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿上他的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.26,0:40:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
