Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.56,0:40:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-艾迪呢  -快走
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.89,0:40:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.37,0:40:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱现在就走  多克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.95,0:40:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.49,0:40:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不行  -快停车
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.77,0:41:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续开
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.87,0:41:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  麦克  麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.19,0:41:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能就这么走了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.97,0:41:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.06,0:41:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.81,0:41:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.78,0:42:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶蝴蝶  无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶蝴蝶  飞飞飞飞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.08,0:42:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三只小蝴蝶  绕着你跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.23,0:42:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只飞走了  还剩下两只
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.68,0:42:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两只小蝴蝶  晒着日光浴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.01,0:42:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只飞走了  只剩下一只
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.43,0:42:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直小蝴蝶  终日独徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.93,0:42:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶飞走了  它们都走了
